{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pallets/click/issues/674","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pallets/click","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pallets/click/issues/674/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pallets/click/issues/674/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pallets/click/issues/674/events","html_url":"https://github.com/pallets/click/issues/674","id":183806740,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUxODM4MDY3NDA=","number":674,"title":"Argument.make_metavar ignores ParamType.get_metavar ; is not configurable to fix","user":{"login":"sirosen","id":1300022,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzMDAwMjI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1300022?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/sirosen","html_url":"https://github.com/sirosen","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sirosen/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sirosen/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sirosen/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sirosen/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sirosen/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sirosen/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sirosen/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sirosen/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sirosen/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":true,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2016-10-18T21:23:00Z","updated_at":"2020-11-13T09:31:01Z","closed_at":"2018-05-15T12:53:02Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":"resolved","sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"If you do the following, you get bad behavior:\n\n``` python\nclass MyType(click.ParamType):\n    def get_metavar(self, param):\n        return \"MY_TYPE\"\n\n@click.command(\"foo\")\n@click.help_option()\n@click.argument(\"param\", type=MyType())\ndef foo_command(param):\n    pass\n```\n\n`foo --help` produces a metavar of `PARAM` instead of the more logically correct `MY_TYPE`.\n\nThis is because `Argument.make_metavar` never looks at `self.type.get_metavar(self)`.\n\nEither this should be fixed so that `Argument.make_metavar` uses the type metavar by default, or `Argument.make_metavar` should take a parameter that lets you toggle between the default \"name\" metavar and the type's default metavar.\n","closed_by":{"login":"JosiahDub","id":8227547,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjgyMjc1NDc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8227547?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/JosiahDub","html_url":"https://github.com/JosiahDub","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JosiahDub/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JosiahDub/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JosiahDub/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JosiahDub/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JosiahDub/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JosiahDub/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JosiahDub/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JosiahDub/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JosiahDub/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pallets/click/issues/674/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pallets/click/issues/674/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}